Paint Pot is the largest Prominent Paint distributors in Limpopo, with 30 years of experience. With three branches in Limpopo they are never far away to assist customers. It’s competition time with Paint Pot. A lucky customer can win a brand new Toyota Aygo. All you have to do is to spend R3 500 in-store and enter the Win-A-Car Lucky Draw. The more you spend, the more entries you will receive. The competition is organised by the Paint Pot Group and customers can enter at branches in Polokwane, Tzaneen, Giyani and Midrand. The competition opened on Monday, 14 June and will end on 24 December with the lucky draw on 30 December. In the case of a stock returned for a cash refund, the original sale ticket will be cancelled. Only tickets placed in the entry box provided at each store, will be used in the draw. The competition is open to all South Africans, with a valid South African ID and older than 18 years. For more details visit Paint Pot’s Facebook page, Paint Pot Group, or their website www.paintpotgroup.co.za. 